{"id":593,"date":"2020-11-13T11:30:43","date_gmt":"2020-11-13T10:30:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/?p=593"},"modified":"2020-11-15T16:14:37","modified_gmt":"2020-11-15T15:14:37","slug":"triple-at-the-realising-the-european-open-science-cloud-event","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/2020\/11\/triple-at-the-realising-the-european-open-science-cloud-event\/","title":{"rendered":"TRIPLE at the &#8220;Realising the European Open Science Cloud&#8221; event"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<p>From 16-19 November, you can find out more about the TRIPLE project and the GOTRIPLE platform by visiting the &#8220;Realising the European Open Science Cloud&#8221; joint event by the <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/sshopencloud.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\">SSHOC<\/a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.eosc-portal.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\">EOSC<\/a> and <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.project-freya.eu\/en\" target=\"_blank\">FREYA project<\/a>s. Participation at this event is free &#8211; register here: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.eosc-hub.eu\/events\/realising-european-open-science-cloud\/eosc-projects-expo\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.eosc-hub.eu\/events\/realising-european-open-science-cloud\/eosc-projects-expo<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>TRIPLE booth at the &#8220;EOSC Projects EXPO&#8221;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Come and visit our booth &#8220;<strong>The SSH discovery platform GOTRIPLE:<\/strong> <strong>A future EOSC service<\/strong>&#8221; at the <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.eosc-hub.eu\/events\/realising-european-open-science-cloud\/eosc-projects-expo\" target=\"_blank\">&#8220;EOSC Projects EXPO&#8221;<\/a> in the virtual exhibition hall.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-1 wp-block-gallery aligncent