image-597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-4_ImpactsGoals-240x300.png 240w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-4_ImpactsGoals-819x1024.png 819w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-4_ImpactsGoals-768x960.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-4_ImpactsGoals-1229x1536.png 1229w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-4_ImpactsGoals-1638x2048.png 1638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Impacts &amp; goals of TRIPLE<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"240\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages-240x300.png\" alt=\"TRIPLE Work Packages\" data-id=\"600\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages.png\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/?attachment_id=600\" class=\"wp-image-600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages-240x300.png 240w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages-819x1024.png 819w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages-768x960.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages-1229x1536.png 1229w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-2_WorkPackages-1638x2048.png 1638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">The TRIPLE work packages<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"240\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships-240x300.png\" alt=\"TRIPLE relationships\" data-id=\"596\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships.png\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/?attachment_id=596\" class=\"wp-image-596\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships-240x300.png 240w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships-819x1024.png 819w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships-768x960.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships-1229x1536.png 1229w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/TRIPLE-Poster-3_TRIPLErelationships-1638x2048.png 1638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">TRIPLE relationships<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption\">The TRIPLE booth posters<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>At the following times, TRIPLE staff will be available for a chat:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Mon, 16 Nov.: 9:30-11:00 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.huma-num.fr\/\" target=\"_blank\">Hum-Num<\/a>, project management)<\/li><li>Mon, 16 Nov.: 11:00-11:30 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cnr.it\/en\" target=\"_blank\">ILC\/CNR<\/a>, Open Science and EOSC integration)<\/li><li>Mon, 16 Nov.: 11:30-12:30 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.huma-num.fr\/\" target=\"_blank\">Hum-Num<\/a>, project management)<\/li><li>Mon, 16 Nov. .: 12:30-14:30 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.abertay.ac.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\">Abertay University<\/a>, co-design &amp; user research)<\/li><li>Tue, 17 Nov.: 9:30-12:30 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.netseven.it\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\">Net7<\/a>, TRIPLE platform development and innovative services)<\/li><li>Wed, 18 Nov.: 9:30-12:30 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.netseven.it\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\">Net7<\/a>, TRIPLE platform development and innovative services)<\/li><li>Wed, 18 Nov.: 12:30-14:30 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cnr.it\/en\" target=\"_blank\">ILC\/CNR<\/a>, Open Science and EOSC integration)<\/li><li>Thu, 19 Nov.: 9:30-12:30 (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.maxweberstiftung.de\/en\/startseite.html\" target=\"_blank\">MWS<\/a>, communication)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>TRIPLE-SSHOC Workshop<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>On 17 November, 14:00 &#8211; 15:30 CET, there will be a joint workshop organised by TRIPLE and SSHOC, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.eosc-hub.eu\/events\/realising-european-open-science-cloud\/thematic-discovery-portals-eosc-exploring-ssh-data-landscape\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>&#8220;Exploring the SSH data landscape: thematic discovery portals in the EOSC&#8221;<\/strong><\/a>, chaired by Laure Barbot and Yoann Moranville from TRIPLE partner <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.dariah.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\">DARIAH<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/PP-SSHOC-TRIPLE-1024x571.png\" alt=\"Screenshot of SSHOC-TRIPLE presentation slide\" class=\"wp-image-611\" width=\"474\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/PP-SSHOC-TRIPLE-1024x571.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/PP-SSHOC-TRIPLE-300x167.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/PP-SSHOC-TRIPLE-768x428.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/PP-SSHOC-TRIPLE.png 1148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>This workshop is an opportunity to connect two discovery portals for social sciences and humanities resources that are developed in the EOSC context via the SSHOC and the TRIPLE projects: the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.sshopencloud.eu\/ssh-open-marketplace\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SSH Open Marketplace<\/a> and the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.gotriple.eu\/?p=544\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">GOTRIPLE platform<\/a>. During this event, we will investigate synergies and collaborations and talk about how to avoid data silos. The main objectives of this workshop are to:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Address the way GOTRIPLE and the SSH Open Marketplace are dealing with SSH data, especially with datasets and publications<\/li><li>Involve people from the technical teams of both projects to explore the ways we could envision to connect the two platforms<\/li><li>Share expertise<\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>From 16-19 November, you can find out more about the TRIPLE project and the GOTRIPLE platform by visiting the &#8220;Realising the European Open Science Cloud&#8221; joint event by the SSHOC, EOSC and FREYA projects. Participation at this event is free<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":595,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[4,8],"tags":[13],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/593"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotrip